種，第一，我要試吓先，我又唔想話&hellip;&hellip;你接完種之後加咗好多副作用，啲感冒症狀啊&hellip;&hellip;脹痛！紅腫！痕癢！結果啲市民出嚟一定鬧我，根本無呢種疫苗！咁就證明上面嗰個係流嘅&hellip;&hellip;我話要畀我試吓先。後來我經過都知道佢哋係用國產疫苗嘅，而且無加嗰啲咩化學嘅嘢。就係咁&hellip;&hellip;啪咗呢個月&hellip;&hellip;咁呢個月落嚟之後又點呢&hellip;&hellip;起碼我用咗好舒服。依家呢&hellip;&hellip;日日都重用緊佢！日日都係用佢呢&hellip;&hellip;我重比我成家班用！嚟！嚟！嚟！大家試吓啦！"},{"pid":"78379cfd6f18cb6e8245e1e456f17ae773bd1a78","tid":2375202,"uid":49329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T05:42:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}